## Yang Dikerjakan

### 1.1 — Fix Semua Models (13 model)

Semua model yang kosong/error telah diperbaiki secara menyeluruh dengan **fillable**, **relasi Eloquent**, **$casts**, dan **SoftDeletes** yang lengkap.

| Model | Bug Lama | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| [WaliSantri](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/WaliSantri.php#16-67) | Missing `use BelongsTo/HasMany` → Fatal Error | Tambah use statements + SoftDeletes + fillable |
| [Student](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/Student.php#20-101) | Tidak ada SoftDeletes, relasi kurang | Tambah SoftDeletes + relasi histories, attendances, grades |
| [Teacher](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/Teacher.php#20-63) | Model kosong total | Fillable + SoftDeletes + is_active + relasi user & assignments |
| [User](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/User.php#24-112) | Fillable tidak ada `role`, `education_level_id` | Update fillable + helper method [isSuperAdmin()](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/User.php#69-78), [isGuru()](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/User.php#79-87) |
| [AcademicYear](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/AcademicYear.php#15-68) | Model kosong | Fillable + casts boolean `is_active` + 3 relasi HasMany |
| [GradeLevel](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/GradeLevel.php#18-63) | Model kosong | Fillable `nama_tingkat` + relasi ke classrooms & curriculums |
| [Classroom](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/Classroom.php#18-81) | Model kosong | Fillable + relasi waliKelas (FK khusus) + semua HasMany |
| [Subject](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/Subject.php#18-43) | Model kosong | Fillable + relasi ke curriculums |
| [Curriculum](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/Curriculum.php#23-84) | Model kosong | Fillable + 5 relasi (pivot utama) |
| [StudentHistory](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/StudentHistory.php#24-65) | Model kosong | Fillable + 3 relasi BelongsTo |
| [TeacherAssignment](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/TeacherAssignment.php#21-79) | Model kosong | Fillable + casts is_wali_kelas + 4 relasi |
| [Attendance](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/Attendance.php#22-63) | Model kosong | Fillable + casts tanggal + 2 relasi |
| [Grade](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/Grade.php#25-67) | Model kosong | Fillable + casts float nilai + 2 relasi |

### 1.2 — Fix Migrations (6 file)

Migrations diselaraskan dengan PRD sebagai sumber kebenaran tunggal:

| Migration | Perubahan |
|---|---|
| `education_levels` | `kode_tingkat` → `kode`, `nama_tingkat` → `nama` |
| `users` | `username` → `name`+`email`; fix enum `role` sesuai PRD; tambah `email_verified_at` + `softDeletes` |
| `academic_years` | `kuartal enum(1,2,3)` → `semester enum(Ganjil,Genap)` |
| [classrooms](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/GradeLevel.php#43-52) | Nama tabel `'classes'` → `'classrooms'` |
| `student_histories` | FK `constrained('classes')` → `constrained('classrooms')` |
| `teacher_assignments` | FK `constrained('classes')` → `constrained('classrooms')` |
| [attendances](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Models/Classroom.php#72-80) | FK `constrained('classes')` → `constrained('classrooms')` |

### 1.3 — Sistem Autentikasi & RBAC

**File-file baru yang dibuat:**

| File | Fungsi |
|---|---|
| [app/Http/Middleware/RoleMiddleware.php](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Http/Middleware/RoleMiddleware.php) | Guard RBAC — validasi role user vs role yang diizinkan di route |
| [app/Http/Controllers/Auth/LoginController.php](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Http/Controllers/Auth/LoginController.php) | Login (dengan session regeneration) + Logout (3 langkah keamanan) |
| [app/Http/Controllers/DashboardController.php](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/app/Http/Controllers/DashboardController.php) | Dashboard adaptif per role |
| [resources/views/auth/login.blade.php](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/resources/views/auth/login.blade.php) | Halaman login premium (gradient indigo, animasi) |
| [resources/views/dashboard.blade.php](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/resources/views/dashboard.blade.php) | Dashboard dengan sidebar navigasi dinamis per role |
| [routes/web.php](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/routes/web.php) | Routes terstruktur: guest group + auth group |
| [bootstrap/app.php](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/bootstrap/app.php) | Registrasi alias middleware `'role'` |

### 1.4 — Seeders Data Awal

**3 file seeder baru:**
- [EducationLevelSeeder](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/database/seeders/EducationLevelSeeder.php#21-45) — 4 unit: TK, MI, MTs, Ulya
- [UserSeeder](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/database/seeders/UserSeeder.php#23-45) — Super Admin: `superadmin@simad.sch.id`
- [AcademicYearSeeder](file:///Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/simad-app/database/seeders/AcademicYearSeeder.php#18-37) — Tahun Ajaran 2025/2026 Semester Ganjil (aktif)

