## Arsitektur Relasi Antar Model

```mermaid
erDiagram
    EducationLevel ||--o{ GradeLevel : has
    EducationLevel ||--o{ Student : "current_level"
    EducationLevel ||--o{ User : scoped_to
    GradeLevel ||--o{ Classroom : has
    GradeLevel ||--o{ Curriculum : has
    Classroom ||--o{ StudentHistory : in
    Classroom ||--o{ TeacherAssignment : taught_in
    Classroom ||--o{ Attendance : recorded_in
    AcademicYear ||--o{ Curriculum : defines
    AcademicYear ||--o{ StudentHistory : period
    AcademicYear ||--o{ TeacherAssignment : period
    Subject ||--o{ Curriculum : included_in
    Curriculum ||--o{ Grade : scored_via
    Curriculum ||--o{ TeacherAssignment : assigned_via
    Student ||--o{ StudentHistory : has
    Student ||--o{ Attendance : has
    Student ||--o{ Grade : receives
    WaliSantri ||--o{ Student : guardian_of
    Teacher ||--o{ TeacherAssignment : assigned
    User ||--o| Teacher : profile
    User ||--o| WaliSantri : account
```
